[{"id":"VH919812","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Consider the following code segment.</p><div class=\"standalone_code style:1\"><p class=\"code_line indent:0\">int[] arr = {4, 3, 2, 1, 0};</p><p class=\"code_line indent:0\">int total = 0;</p><p class=\"code_line indent:0\">for (int k = 0; k &lt;= total; k++)</p><p class=\"code_line indent:0\">{</p><p class=\"code_line indent:3\">if (arr[k] % 2 == 0)</p><p class=\"code_line indent:3\">{</p><p class=\"code_line indent:6\">total += arr[k];</p><p class=\"code_line indent:3\">}</p><p class=\"code_line indent:3\">else</p><p class=\"code_line indent:3\">{</p><p class=\"code_line indent:6\">total -= arr[k];</p><p class=\"code_line indent:3\">}</p><p class=\"code_line indent:0\">}</p><p class=\"code_line indent:0\">System.out.print(total);</p></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">What, if anything, is printed as a result of executing the code segment?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH919812_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">2</span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">1</span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_code\">0</span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Nothing is printed because the code segment causes a runtime error.</p>"],"answer":1}]